---
layout: base
title: "Portal de Apostilas Digitais"
---

<div class="portal-container">
  <header class="portal-header">
    <h1>Portal de Apostilas Digitais</h1>
    <p>Acesse o conteúdo dos cursos de forma organizada e dinâmica.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="subject-grid">
    {% for subject in collections.subjects %}
    <a href="{{ subject.url | url }}" class="subject-card">
      <div class="subject-info">
        <h2>{{ subject.data.subject_title }}</h2>

        <p>{{ subject.data.subject_description }}</p>
        <span class="subject-status">{{ subject.data.subject_status or "Disponível" }}</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</div>

